And great earthquakes shall be in divers places, and famines, and pestilences; and fearful sights and great signs shall there be from heaven - Luke 21:11 KJV

Not to spread any fear but it's about to get real. Just as many people warned us, the ""Cornavirus"" is now officially in the U.S.A. & the city of San Francisco has declared a state of emergency. If you haven't put your faith in God, now is the time. Don't wait for things to get worse. The coronavirus has hit American soil, & all the people calling this fake, claiming we're spreading fear & mass panick, will get to see how this all turns out. Prophecies of the Bible are happening before our eyes. I believe we are witnessing the 6th & 7th Seals of Revelation, just not opened as yet - Revelation 7

Hopefully martial law isn't declared but it seems inevitable. All the concentration camps, FEMA stations, & guillotines are ready & in place for the Great Tribulation. If you don't believe me go & do your research. Billions of dollars have been invested into this for several years now. Please heed the warnings & do not take this as a joke. May God bless & have mercy on all of us.
